'''''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'' 4''' is the fourth issue of [[Star Wars Insider|''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'']], later rebranded as the ''Star Wars Insider''. Issue 4 was published in Summer [[1988]].

{{Magazine-stub|issue}}

==Contents==
===Features===
*"''Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade''"
*"[[Warwick Davis: An Unlikely Hero]]" {{C|by [[Dan Madsen]] & John S. Davis}}
*"The Novelization of ''Tucker: The Man & His Dreams''" by John S. Davis
*"Ron Howard: Imagining The Wonders of ''Willow''" by Dan Madsen
*"Attracting the Very Best: A Look at the Cast and Crew of ''Tucker''" by [[Lisa E. Cowan]]

===Departments===
*"The Fan Forum"
*"[[Inside ILM]]: Creating the Magic of ''Willow''" {{C|by [[John S. Davis]]}}

